-- Berkshire RV Unit Acquires Majority Stake in Spartan Facility
-- B y   N o a h   B u h a y a r
-- 2013-01-07T22:31:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-07/berkshire-rv-unit-acquires-majority-stake-in-spartan-facility.html
Forest River, the recreational
vehicle unit owned by  Warren Buffett ’s Berkshire Hathaway Inc.,
bought the majority of a Wakarusa, Indiana, facility owned by
 Spartan Motors Inc. (SPAR)   The deal is part of Spartan’s plan to consolidate
facilities, the Charlotte, Michigan-based seller said today in a
regulatory filing.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Noah Buhayar in New York at 
